{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How does Saskatchewan business funding work?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Saskatchewan operates a strategically focused business funding ecosystem with approximately $425 million\n                  available annually through provincial programs. The province's economic development priorities\n                  center on agriculture, mining, energy, and emerging technology sectors—reflecting Saskatchewan's\n                  natural resource strengths and diversification ambitions.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Innovation Saskatchewan serves as the province's primary innovation agency, coordinating\n                  technology development and commercialization support. The Ministry of Trade and Export Development\n                  manages export-focused programs, while the Ministry of Agriculture oversees significant funding\n                  for agricultural value-added projects—one of Canada's most substantial agricultural\n                  business support programs.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Saskatchewan's smaller population means less competition\n                    for business funding compared to Ontario, BC, or Alberta. Businesses in priority sectors\n                    like agriculture, potash mining technology, and clean energy often see approval rates\n                    significantly above national averages.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">What are the major Saskatchewan grant programs?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                {/* Innovation Saskatchewan */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Innovation Saskatchewan Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$25K - $300K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Innovation</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Innovation Saskatchewan coordinates the province's innovation ecosystem,\n                      providing funding for R&D, technology commercialization, and startup development.\n                      Programs include direct grants and connections to federal funding sources.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Research and development projects</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Technology commercialization</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Startup accelerator programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Agriculture Value-Added Fund */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Agriculture Value-Added Fund</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $500K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Agriculture</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      One of Canada's most substantial agricultural business funds, supporting\n                      value-added processing, food manufacturing, and agricultural product development.\n                      Saskatchewan's agricultural heritage makes this a well-resourced program.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Food processing and manufacturing</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Agricultural product development</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Value-chain integration</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Export Development Program */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Export Development Program</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $75K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Export Focus</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Support for Saskatchewan businesses expanding into international markets.\n                      Covers market research, trade mission participation, and export readiness\n                      activities. Particularly relevant for agricultural and resource exporters.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Market research and development</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Trade mission participation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Export readiness training</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Saskatchewan Small Business Loans */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Community Futures Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $150K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Regional</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Community Futures organizations across Saskatchewan provide loans, grants,\n                      and business support services for rural and small-town businesses. Each\n                      regional office has some flexibility in program delivery.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Low-interest business loans</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Business advisory services</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Rural community focus</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for Saskatchewan Business Grants?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Saskatchewan business grants are available to for-profit enterprises operating within the province.\n                Eligibility varies by program, but most require Saskatchewan incorporation or significant\n                provincial operations. Agricultural projects often have additional eligibility through\n                federal-provincial cost-share programs.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Incorporated in Saskatchewan or with significant local operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Small and medium enterprises (under 500 employees)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses in priority sectors (agriculture, mining, technology)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Good standing with provincial and federal tax authorities</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects with demonstrable economic impact</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Ineligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses without Saskatchewan operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects completed before application</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses in tax arrears</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Real estate speculation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Primary agricultural production (most grants for value-added only)</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Grant Funding Can Saskatchewan Businesses Get?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Saskatchewan grant amounts vary by program and project scope. Agricultural value-added\n                projects can access significant funding, while innovation and export programs offer\n                more modest amounts but with less stringent requirements.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-yellow-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Typical Range</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Cost Share</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Export Development</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$5K - $75K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Innovation Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$25K - $300K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">33-50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Ag Value-Added</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$100K - $500K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">25-50%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Community Futures</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$10K - $150K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Loan basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Saskatchewan businesses can stack provincial funding with\n                  federal programs. PrairiesCan (formerly Western Economic Diversification) offers\n                  additional federal funding specifically for Prairie provinces, while IRAP and\n                  SR&ED provide technology-focused support.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How to Apply for Saskatchewan Business Grants - Step by Step</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Research Programs (1-2 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Visit Innovation Saskatchewan and Ministry of Trade websites for program details.\n                      For agricultural projects, check the Ministry of Agriculture's Agri-Business\n                      section for value-added funding opportunities.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Pre-Application Consultation</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Saskatchewan programs typically offer intake consultations. For Innovation\n                      Saskatchewan programs, connect with their intake team. Agricultural projects\n                      should consult with regional Agriculture offices.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Application (2-3 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Complete application forms with business plan, project description, timeline,\n                      and budget. Saskatchewan applications are typically 10-20 pages. Agricultural\n                      programs may require additional production and processing documentation.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit & Review</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Submit through provincial intake portals. Most programs have 45-75 day\n                      review periods. Be responsive to follow-up requests—program officers\n                      may ask for clarification or additional documentation.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">5</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Contribution Agreement</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Upon approval, sign a contribution agreement outlining terms, milestones,\n                      and reporting requirements. Saskatchewan typically uses reimbursement-based\n                      funding—you spend first, then claim back eligible expenses.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required for Saskatchewan Grant Applications?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Core Business Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Saskatchewan corporate registration</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>2-3 years of financial statements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Current year-to-date financials</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Bank statements (last 6 months)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project-Specific Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Detailed project plan with milestones</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Budget with vendor quotes</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Market analysis</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Letters of support (for ag projects)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does Saskatchewan Grant Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-yellow-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Review Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">First Payment</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Export Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Upon claim</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Innovation Saskatchewan</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">45-60 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Milestone basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Ag Value-Added</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">60-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Reimbursement</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Note:</strong> Most Saskatchewan programs accept applications on a\n                  continuous intake basis. Check the official provincial websites for current\n                  program status and any temporary closures.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Common Mistakes to Avoid with Saskatchewan Grant Applications</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Confusing Primary Production with Value-Added</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Most Saskatchewan agricultural grants fund value-added processing, not\n                          primary production. Growing crops doesn't qualify—processing them into\n                          food products does. Make sure you understand this distinction.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Weak Export Market Documentation</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Export development grants require evidence of export readiness and market\n                          opportunity. Vague statements about \"international expansion\" aren't\n                          sufficient—provide specific target markets and entry strategies.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Not Demonstrating Matching Funds</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Most Saskatchewan grants require you to co-invest 50-75% of costs.\n                          Show clear evidence of matching capital through bank statements or\n                          investor commitments.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Which industries get the most Saskatchewan funding?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Agriculture & Agri-Food</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Food processing, pulse crops, specialty grains, and AgTech</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Mining & Resources</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Potash, uranium, oil services, and mining technology</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Technology</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">AgTech, clean technology, software, and digital innovation</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Clean Energy</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Renewable energy, carbon capture, and sustainability</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Life Sciences</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Vaccine development, animal health, and biopharmaceuticals</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Indigenous Business</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Specialized programs for Indigenous entrepreneurs</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Are there local grants in Saskatoon and Regina?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Saskatoon Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Co.Labs – Innovation accelerator</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Saskatoon Regional Economic Development Authority</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>University of Saskatchewan commercialization</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Regina Programs</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Economic Development Regina</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Cultivator – AgTech accelerator</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>University of Regina innovation programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What if I don't qualify for Saskatchewan grants?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SR&ED Tax Credits</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal R&D credits provide 35-64% return on eligible costs. Saskatchewan\n                    offers an additional 10% provincial R&D tax credit for qualifying activities.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sred-scientific-research-experimental-development\">\n                    Learn about SR&ED →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">PrairiesCan (Federal)</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal regional development agency for Prairie provinces. Offers substantial\n                    funding for innovation, economic development, and diversification.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
  "shortAnswer": "Yes — Complete guide to Saskatchewan small business grants. Access Saskatchewan Small Business Loans, Innovation Saskatchewan Programs, Agriculture Value-Added Fund, and Export Development programs. Funding available: up to $425M+.",
  "shortAnswerQuestion": "What small business grants are available in 2026?",
  "faq": [
    {
      "question": "What is the application deadline for Saskatchewan Small Business Grants  | + SME Growth Programs in 2026?",
      "answer": "Deadlines typically vary by specific program tier. However, for 2026, many initiatives operate on a rolling intake basis until funds are depleted. Check the official portal for specific cutoffs."
    },
    {
      "question": "How much funding can I get through Saskatchewan Small Business Grants  | + SME Growth Programs?",
      "answer": "Funding amounts range depending on business size and scope. Top awards can reach $425M."
